name: Incline Dumbbell Press
steps: Set bench to 30–45° incline.
Press dumbbells overhead at slight angle.
Lower until elbows are at 90°, then press up.

name: Machine Chest Press
steps: Adjust seat so handles are chest height.
Push handles forward until arms are extended.
Control back to starting position.

name: Deadlift
steps: Stand with mid-foot under barbell.
Hinge hips back and grip bar just outside knees.
Drive hips forward and lift bar standing tall.

name: Cable Lateral Raise
steps: Set cable to lowest setting with single handle.
Raise arm to side until shoulder height.
Lower slowly with control.

name: EZ Bar Curl
steps: Hold EZ bar with palms facing up.
Curl bar toward shoulders without swinging.
Lower slowly.

name: Dips
steps: Grasp parallel bars, lower body by bending elbows.
Push back up to lockout.
Keep torso leaning slightly forward.

name: Goblet Squat
steps: Hold a dumbbell close to chest.
Squat down keeping chest upright.
Drive through heels to stand up.

name: Walking Lunges
steps: Hold dumbbells at sides.
Step forward and lower until back knee nearly touches ground.
Push through front heel and repeat on other side.

name: Bulgarian Split Squat
steps: Place rear foot on bench behind you.
Lower front thigh until parallel.
Drive through front foot to return.

name: Mountain Climbers
steps: Start in plank position.
Drive knees alternately toward chest.
Maintain fast pace with tight core.

name: Farmer's Carry
steps: Hold heavy weights at sides.
Walk forward keeping shoulders back.
Maintain tight core throughout.

name: Medicine Ball Slam
steps: Lift ball overhead with arms extended.
Slam ball down into ground as hard as possible.
Squat to pick up and repeat.

name: Pallof Press
steps: Hold cable/band at chest height.
Press hands forward resisting rotation.
Hold for a beat and bring hands back.

name: Face Pull
steps: Set rope attachment at face height.
Pull rope towards face, elbows flared out.
Squeeze upper back muscles.
